                    "items": [
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": "<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/f/fd3cb58f280a8de4271428adfc7f19f69fe28fea.png\" class=\"height-200-pixels width-200-pixels float-right\"/>Maak nu de volgende eindexamenvragen uit ExamenKracht.<br/>\nGebruik de aanpak die je hiervoor geleerd hebt.</p>\n<h4>VMBO-KGT34 Open vragen</h4>\n<table cellpadding=\"5\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/f/fd3cb58f280a8de4271428adfc7f19f69fe28fea.png\" class=\"height-41-pixels width-40-pixels float-right\"/></td>\n<td><strong><a class=\"content-link-button\" href=\"https://mijn.vo-content.nl/examenkracht/extern/vraag/9389\" target=\"_blank\">DUI 2021-1 Vraag 5</a></strong></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table cellpadding=\"5\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/f/fd3cb58f280a8de4271428adfc7f19f69fe28fea.png\" class=\"height-41-pixels width-40-pixels float-right\"/></td>\n<td><strong><a class=\"content-link-button\" href=\"https://mijn.vo-content.nl/examenkracht/extern/vraag/501\" target=\"_blank\">DUI 2021-1 Vraag 15</a></strong></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table cellpadding=\"5\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/f/fd3cb58f280a8de4271428adfc7f19f69fe28fea.png\" class=\"height-41-pixels width-40-pixels float-right\"/></td>\n<td><strong><a class=\"content-link-button\" href=\"https://mijn.vo-content.nl/examenkracht/extern/vraag/9418\" target=\"_blank\">DUI 2021-1 Vraag 26</a></strong></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n"
